---
title: Steak in Balsamic Mushroom Sauce with Roasted Veggies and Smashed Potatoes
description: Balsamic glaze gives this mushroom sauce an Italian-style sweet and savoury flare. Garlic smashed potatoes are perfect for catching what doesn't stay on the perfectly cooked steak!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-in-balsamic-mushroom-sauce-54278e5e-a85f39e8.jpg
